Classes in net.jxta.impl.cm that implement RendezvousListener
 class SrdiManager
          An SrdiManager provides SRDI functionalities such as :

pushing of SRDI messages to a another peer/propagate replication of an SRDI Message to other peers in a given peerview given an expression SRDI provides a independently calculated starting point Forwarding a ResolverQuery, and taking care of hopCount, random selection registers with the RendezvousService to determine when to share SrdSRDIi Entries and whether to push deltas, or full a index provides a SrdiPushEntriesInterface to push SRDI entries

If SrdiManager is started as a thread it performs periodic SRDI pushes of indices and also has the ability to respond to rendezvous events.
